/.github/skills/
/.github/agents/
/.github/workflows/
/.github/copilot-instructions.md
/.github/get-shit-done/
/.github/gsd-file-manifest.json

# Audit documents (contain sensitive architecture and vulnerability details)
/AUDIT.md
.agent
.planning/
